kadjusted returns and capital preservation for our clients our team of approximately  employees constitutes one of the largest in the industry these professionals’ deep reservoir of credit expertise and experience across market cycles is further enhanced by access to blackstone’s global resources and perspective as the supply of available capital is constrained by changes in financial industry regulation and global credit market conditions gso looks forward to continuing to provide financing solutions that enable companies to remain viable – and vital to their employees and communities – for the long term a message from bennett goodman cofounder of gso scale our scale and expertise allow gso to provide financing solutions that enhance a corporation’s financial flexibility while capturing opportunities for our investors range of disciplines the solutions we offer are often not available elsewhere in the credit markets and draw upon a range of noninvestment grade disciplines including leveraged loans high yield bonds distressed debt mezzanine lending and rescue financing providing solutions gso has provided more than  billion in capital in privately originated transactions to enable companies to remain viable billion total assets under management “ “providing credit to companies that might not otherwise have access to capital helps stabilize viable businesses and enables businesses to grow while producing attractive returns for our investors”  bennett goodman senior managing director and cofounder of gso gso gso seeks to generate attractive riskadjusted returns by investing in a broad array of public and private corporate credit instruments across multiple strategies as one of the world’s largest credit investors our activities range from providing private capital to companies when other funding sources are unavailable to investing in public debt securities that are either undervalued or represent attractive riskadjusted returns our approach disciplined strategy our investment strategy revolves around a disciplined credit review process and is founded on the belief that a deep understanding of companies and the industries in which they operate is critical to generating positive total returns and preserving principle deep expertise gso is recognized for our specialized credit expertise and leading global leveraged finance franchise we have a long track record of developing creative valueadditive solutions to address a corporation’s capital structure requirements diversification engaging across a broad array of strategies in the corporate credit markets gso manages funds focusing on leveraged loans high yield bonds distressed debt rescue financing and mezzanine lending synergy gso’s position within blackstone enhances the firm’s reach and resources providing access to extensive industry expertise new sources of capital and a vast global network capital preservation gso aims to minimize downside risk and protect principal by maintaining a diversified portfolio performing intensive credit research and actively monitoring all investments all numbers are as of june   blackstone and gso were featured in an institutional investor profile “blackstone group’s gso capital lenders of last resort” view article  billion assets under management with  billion of assets under management encompassing a range of investment strategies gso is one of the world’s largest creditoriented alternative asset managers our footprint is global with approximately  employees in new york london dublin and houston gso capital partners  billion aum alternative investment funds  billion aum mezzanine  energy funds  billion stressed  distressed funds  billion event driven strategies  billion small cap direct lending funds  billion customized credit strategies  long only  billion aum clos  billion listed funds commingled funds and smas  billion back to top quick links explore blackstone get in touch   the blackstone group lp  english   chinese transparency  disclosur